{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/925460/extras/horizontal_strips-30_spacing.png?t=1727788538\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A CAPTIVATING ATMOSPHERE</h2>Welcome to the psychedelic world of Vectronom: experience waves of color and a pulsing geometric path <strong>that changes with the beat</strong>! All set to a hypnotic electronic soundtrack. There\u2019s only one thing to do: turn up the volume and go with the flow.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/925460/extras/horizontal_strips-31_spacing.png?t=1727788538\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SOLVE PUZZLES AT THE SPEED OF SOUND</h2>Find your path through an ever-changing world, keeping the rhythm with every move you make. Think it sounds easy? The highly intuitive and addictive gameplay will keep you moving through daunting challenges... But how long will you last when the challenges get trickier and trickier? Better play to find out!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/925460/extras/horizontal_strips-32_spacing.png?t=1727788538\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PLAY ON YOUR OWN OR WITH FRIENDS</h2>Set off on a solo campaign with just your headphones for company, or invite a few friends to join the party! \u266a UNTZ! UNTZ! UNTZ! \u266a<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/925460/extras/horizontal_strips-33_spacing.png?t=1727788538\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BUILD YOUR OWN RHYTHMIC RIDDLES</h2>Create your own levels share them and play the creations of others. Vectronom features a fully-fledged level editor which will allow you to build mind bending musical puzzles.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/925460/extras/horizontal_strips-34_spacing_level_editor.png?t=1727788538\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A challenging solo campaign that will completely entrance you<br></li><li>A drop-in, drop-out multiplayer mode that will hypnotize your friends<br></li><li>Colorful and atmospheric levels with a powerful electronic soundtrack<br></li><li>BONUS: the game is compatible with digital dance mats and MIDI instruments, so it won\u2019t just be your fingertips showing off their best moves!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"100%","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/925460/4788cf6737d9e7b0d3c9271f9bd7e0a81a895e27.jpg"},{"name":"Conductor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/925460/94f3b8526f9d9774a0e1431e4665037850a028a1.jpg"},{"name":"Prestissimo","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/925460/a89a33638aea4fd2af8c21a1f8f825bddb7d113d.jpg"},{"name":"Larghetto","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/925460/f027a20f583f4800903ffec8922f598ed352c43b.jpg"},{"name":"Got them","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/925460/d6d236a96d9ea7fcec93a616b42e0b349ff02d65.jpg"},{"name":"Got them quick","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/925460/9997cc47b7f2d61618d842596d77a8fc7a2590e5.jpg"},{"name":"First Try","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/925460/918e118597a3edf0d8cc0efc257b0042859eb4db.jpg"},{"name":"Perfect Tempo","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/925460/3c008b427f931cf2c41292039246e5a5d4a60c1e.jpg"},{"name":"All Pickups","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/925460/48954ed8f1038805477a17bb8ba99ef26d7a8759.jpg"},{"name":"Together","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/925460/69891db3065c5e6b97d73693e038b1f55b69c478.jpg"}],"total":20},"background